components.home.p-1: Marijuana industry is massively expanding as more countries legalize cannabis and market shows no signs of slowing. Industry analysts expect the worldwide legal marijuana market to grow from its current value of $9.2 billion to $57 billion by 2027.
components.home.p-2: Bancannabis is creating the most advanced supply chain in cannabis markets through blockchain solutions and IOT integrations we provide any one in the word the opportunity to be part of this growing market.
components.home.p-3: Our mission is to create the biggest community of innovation and development in cannabis and decentralized solutions related with their supply chain.
